input.code:
json = input['jag_input']
ap_closed_list = []
ap_open_list = []
json.dig('jiorder')&.each do |o|
  if o.dig('header', 'apStatus').downcase == 'close'
    ap_closed_list << o
  else
    ap_open_list << o
  end
end

{
  ap_closed_list: ap_closed_list,
  ap_open_list: ap_open_list  
}
